* &quot;Newcastle is Peru&quot; (1969)
* &quot;Bow Down&quot; (1977)
* &quot;Looking Up&quot; (1979)
* &quot;A Kumquat for John Keats&quot; (1981)
* &quot;The Fire Gap &quot; (1985)
