<doc id="166944" wikidata="Q2926788" url="?curid=166944" title="Bruno Fuligni">
<text>Bruno Fuligni (born 21 May 1968) is a French writer and historian.

==Selected works==
*
*
* &quot;Atlantes des zones extraterrestres&quot; (ed.Flammarion, 2017) 

==References==</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q2926788" start="0" end="13" title="Bruno Fuligni" label="Bruno Fuligni"/>
